{"tid":1311263,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"手頭上有1個2毫半","createTime":"2019-07-13T05:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T06:33:11.000Z","uid":19638,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a29da504729aea11e8a8a603b79bb079366786a7","tid":1311263,"uid":19638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:53:40.000Z","msg":"想問有咩盤可選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好背山面海，水清沙幼。<br />\n<br />\n出入要登記，費事閒雜人等騷擾阻住晒。<br />\n<br />\n另外，想要多個直昇機坪可比我泊架空軍一號。<br />\n<br />\n可以泊埋遊艇就最好。<br />\n<br />\n車庫一定要有，可以泊我架勞斯萊斯。<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多，有咩再後補。<br />\n<br />\n有無經紀可以帶我睇睇類似既盤先，時間可就你。<br />\n<br />\n在線等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45052de719374c29574fbab7cf12aa97cc8771a","tid":1311263,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:00:37.000Z","msg":"赤柱"},{"pid":"8ec44cbdb28038be892c2e0b49a2e6b4f46f1632","tid":1311263,"uid":19638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc4433c531902d1ccd5796f625b82d596c881c9","tid":1311263,"uid":153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:31:02.000Z","msg":"青山"},{"pid":"687c769f287b9daba6ea5d37c0a1ce68292dd1af","tid":1311263,"uid":19638,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0bc4433c531902d1ccd5796f625b82d596c881c9","tid":1311263,"uid":153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:31:02.000Z","msg":"青山"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:33:11.000Z","msg":"無位泊遊艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}